1. *Stalo* mi je da se pošaljem u inostranstvo. (I wanted to go abroad.)
2. *Stalo* nam je da to pitanje bude rešeno što pre. (We wanted that question to be solved as soon as possible.)
3. Ona je *stala* da bi pogledala zalazak sunca. (She stopped to watch the sunset.)
4. On se *stalo* da se uključi u razgovor. (He stopped to join in the conversation.)
5. Svi su *stali* da bi učestvovali u debati. (Everyone stopped to participate in the debate.)